This fast stop was pivotal in Daniel Ricciardo's win 👌

#F1 #Formula1 #Motorsports #ItalianGP @danielricciardo @mclaren @dhlmotorsports #MomentsThatDeliver

Daniel Ricciardo waited three years for this day to come!

This is his story, told by the man himself. Just how impressive was that Monza win?! It is brilliant to see him back on top of the podium again 🏆
